                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Merry</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">San Jose, Costa Rica</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-09-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 22, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Merry reports that the Salvadorean Congress ratified on the 22d instant the
                    agreement for the settlement of the arbitration of the Salvador Commercial
                    Company’s claim.)</p>
            </div>
